                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The Hellknights defensively lock their shields. Until the start of this troop's next turn, the troop and all allies within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] gain a +1 circumstance bonus to their AC and Reflex saving throws.</p>"
